## Description
A bug was found in the following function:
```java
public static int bitcount(int n) {
int count = 0;
while (n != 0) {
    n = (n ^ (n - 1));
        count++;
}
return count;
}
```
The bug is that it performs `(n ^ (n - 1))` instead of `(n & (n - 1))`.

## Fix
The bug can be fixed by using the following code:
```java
public static int bitcount(int n) {
int count = 0;
while (n != 0) {
    n &= n - 1;
        count++;
}
return count;
}
```

